of former Governor Wen Muchen.

00:11:18.800 --> 00:11:20.560
After Wen Muchen was executed,

00:11:20.920 --> 00:11:22.800
Wen Yueqian mysteriously fell ill
and died.

00:11:23.070 --> 00:11:24.470
Wen Yueqian...

